                                                MENUITEM cm_caption ACTION nil NAME cm_name IMAGE cm_image CHECKED DISABLED MESSAGE cm_Message
                                             ELSE
                                                MENUITEM cm_caption ACTION &cm_action NAME cm_name IMAGE cm_image CHECKED DISABLED MESSAGE cm_Message
